<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">
<head>
<title>onselect attribute of textarea element</title>
</head>
<body>
<div><textarea rows="1" cols="20" name="in" onselect="this.value='PASS'">Select this text</textarea></div>
<p>You should see word pass once you select text in textarea above.</p>
</body>
</html>

